### 1. Get Order Details
GET {{protocol}}://{{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/orders/{{orderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 2. Create Payment Session (MIDTRANS SNAP)
# Deterministic Order ID: ORD-YYYYMMDD-XXXX-HASH
POST {{protocol}}://{{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/orders/{{orderId}}/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Idempotency-Key: payment-attempt-001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "MIDTRANS",
  "flow": "SNAP",
  "preferredChannel": "GOPAY",
  "enabledChannels": ["GOPAY", "QRIS", "BANK_TRANSFER"]
}

### 3. Retry Create Payment Session (Idempotent)
# Should return the EXACT same snapToken and providerOrderId
POST {{protocol}}://{{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/orders/{{orderId}}/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Idempotency-Key: payment-attempt-001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "MIDTRANS",
  "flow": "SNAP",
  "preferredChannel": "GOPAY",
  "enabledChannels": ["GOPAY", "QRIS", "BANK_TRANSFER"]
}

### 4. Cancel Order
POST {{protocol}}://{{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/orders/{{orderId}}/cancellations
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Idempotency-Key: cancel-attempt-001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Salah pilih metode pembayaran"
}
